This tool, `cf-ips-to-hcloud-fw`, helps you keep your Hetzner Cloud firewall
rules up-to-date with the current Cloudflare IP ranges.

## Table of Contents <!-- omit in toc -->

- [Overview](#overview)
- [Installation](#installation)
